Consent: KU Leuven Informed ConsentTitle: Candidate PreferencesPrincipal Investigator: Martin LukacCo-Investigator: Alberto Stefanelli ProceduresYou are being asked to take part in a research study. If you decide to take part, you will complete an online survey that will take 15-20 minutes of your time. You may take the survey wherever is convenient for you. CompensationYou will receive compensation as you have previously agreed with your supplier panel Voluntary Participation and WithdrawalYou do not have to be in this study. If you decide to be in the study and change your mind, you have the right to drop out at any time. Contact InformationContact Professor name@surname.edu if you have questions or concerns. ConsentIf you are willing to volunteer for this research, please continue further and click on the Agree button and start the survey.
